{"tid":1790267,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"向示威者擲石及掌摑 兩警濫暴被判入獄","createTime":"2019-12-20T01:20:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-20T01:48:08.000Z","uid":335434,"like":19,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"6e765adf89ac819e6e2e36137b8795947b1145ae","tid":1790267,"uid":335434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T01:20:28.000Z","msg":"兩名法國警員今年5月1日對「黃背心」示威者濫暴，被法庭判處入獄但緩刑，是這場反政府抗爭爆發一年多以來，首次有執法人員被定罪。<br />\n<br />\n其中一名警員因向示威者擲石，被判入獄兩個月，另一名警員因掌摑一名示威者，被判入獄4個月。兩人均獲准緩刑。<br />\n<br />\n兩段呈堂影片顯示首名警員拾起路磚，擲向約8米外的示威者。法庭認為該警員的行為並非自衛，而是試圖向示威者發出「生理和心理上震懾」，令他們停止擲物。警員辯護時說，他當時的行為是出於驚慌而非憤怒，擲石是希望製造安全距離，而不是想傷人。<br />\n<br />\n「黃背心」示威自去年11月爆發以來，外間經常批評法國警察對付示威者的強硬手段。根據官方統計，在多月的示威衝突中，有約2500名示威者和1800名警員受傷。<br />\n<br />\n法新社 <br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20191220/60397558\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191220%2F60397558&d=1CRlZafk7JeE%2BAtxbqKu5ZszS%2Fgy1fqSqMk7TcT3QhU%3D&h=243cf2f1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191220%2F60397558&h=50554d40\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20191220/60397558</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2918779/org/06ad7a650387f5dfdc6dc2f984ecbc83.jpg/cAINnm5PMLRdScCIGKsBGRpiP7LMU4PNOx_mfjsf5n4?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2918779%2Forg%2F06ad7a650387f5dfdc6dc2f984ecbc83.jpg%2FcAINnm5PMLRdScCIGKsBGRpiP7LMU4PNOx_mfjsf5n4%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=899414d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/02/10/110157_3641fb8ea89049311e63e9124afc0215.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F02%2F10%2F110157_3641fb8ea89049311e63e9124afc0215.jpg&h=5d2aac3